  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>1. What Are Cookies</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help us remember your preferences, keep you logged in, understand how you use the platform, and improve your experience. We also use similar technologies including localStorage and session tokens.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>2. Cookie Categories</h2>

    <div class="cookie-category">
      <div class="cookie-category-header">
        <span class="cookie-category-title">Strictly Necessary</span>
        <span class="badge badge-green">Always Active</span>
      </div>
      <p>These cookies are essential for the platform to function. They include session authentication tokens (HTTP-only cookies), CSRF protection tokens, and load balancing cookies. You cannot opt out of these — without them the Service cannot operate.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cookie-category">
      <div class="cookie-category-header">
        <span class="cookie-category-title">Functional / Preference</span>
        <span class="badge badge-amber">Optional</span>
      </div>
      <p>These remember your settings such as dashboard layout, selected filters, timezone preference, and UI theme. Disabling them means your preferences will not be saved between sessions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cookie-category">
      <div class="cookie-category-header">
        <span class="cookie-category-title">Analytics</span>
        <span class="badge badge-amber">Optional</span>
      </div>
      <p>We use privacy-focused analytics (no third-party advertising trackers) to understand how users navigate the platform, which features are used, and where errors occur. Data is aggregated and anonymised. We do not use Google Analytics.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cookie-category">
      <div class="cookie-category-header">
        <span class="cookie-category-title">Marketing / Advertising</span>
        <span class="badge badge-red">Not Used</span>
      </div>
      <p>We do not serve advertising and do not use advertising cookies or third-party marketing trackers on this platform.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>3. Specific Cookies We Set</h2>
