          <td>1 year</td>
          <td><span class="badge badge-green">Necessary</span></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="doc-section">
    <h2>4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p>The following third-party services may set cookies when you interact with certain parts of the platform:</p>
    <table class="cookie-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Service</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Policy</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Stripe</td>
          <td>Payment fraud prevention and checkout session</td>
          <td><a href="https://stripe.com/privacy">stripe.com/privacy</a></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Cloudflare</td>
